title: Another Election Earthquake Last Night (Ep 1790)
description:
In this episode, I address the huge election message sent last night that could resonate through 2024. 

News Picks:


“Politifact” gets destroyed after commenting about red-flag laws. 


Wholesale prices rose 10.8% in May, near a record annual pace.


Squad Member Threatens 'Civil War' If GOP Takes House.

Is COVID causing our immune systems to act differently? 


China is abusing those QR codes, must read.
